## Bug Fixes During Development

| Bug | Root Cause | Fix |
|-----|-----------|-----|
| `restcus=0` for infeasible solutions | Parser only tracked constraint-violated customers, not those missing from decoded routes | Added missing-customer detection in `SolutionParser.parse()` |
| Greedy NN routes destroyed after encoding | [from_routes](file:///g:/BaoCaoLuanVanThs/code/core/solution.py#65-114) used wrong argsort mapping — decode didn't reproduce original routes | Fixed key assignment: `keys[z_val-1] = rank-based key` |
| IndexError in ABS | Separator IDs exceeded nvar bounds | Bounded separators to `[n_c+1, nvar]` range |
| Slow SSO update | Per-element Python loop | Vectorized with `np.where` |

## How to Run

```bash
cd g:\BaoCaoLuanVanThs\code
.\venv\Scripts\activate

# Single instance (quick test)
python main.py --mode single --instance C101 --time 10

# Compare 6 algorithms on one instance
python main.py --mode compare --instance C101 --time 60 --runs 15

# Full 56-instance Solomon benchmark
python main.py --mode full --time 60 --runs 15
```
